etcdctl utility Container
-----------------------

Installation
------------
1. Install AirShip in a Bottle(AIAB)

sudo -i
mkdir -p /root/deploy && cd "$_"
git clone https://git.openstack.org/openstack/airship-in-a-bottle
cd /root/deploy/airship-in-a-bottle/manifests/dev_single_node
./airship-in-a-bottle.sh


2. Deploy Porthole

git clone https://github.com/att-comdev/porthole.git

If not already merged please checkout the below PS.
git pull "ssh://JaganKavva@review.gerrithub.io:29418/att-comdev/porthole" refs/changes/34/454934/17

cd porthole
./install_etcdctl_utility.sh

Usage
-----

Get in to the utility pod using kubectl exec. To perform any operation use the below example. Please be ready with password for accessing below cli commands.

kubectl exec -it <POD_NAME> -n utility /bin/bash

example:
   nccli etcdctl member list
   nccli etcdctl endpoint health
   nccli etcdctl endpoint status
